### GET all users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users

### CREATE user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Organizer One",
  "email": "organizer@test.com"
}

### GET all events
GET http://localhost:8080/api/events

### CREATE event
POST http://localhost:8080/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Event",
  "category": "Music",
  "eventType": "Concert",
  "venue": "Test Venue",
  "address": "Test Address",
  "city": "Athens",
  "country": "Greece",
  "startDateTime": "2025-07-12T20:30:00",
  "endDateTime": "2025-07-12T23:00:00",
  "capacity": 100,
  "status": "DRAFT",
  "description": "Test event",
  "organizer": {
    "id": 1
  }
}